		<h1>Creating a searchable corpus</h1>
		<hr>
	</center>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Corpus:</strong> Collection of documents</li>
		<li><strong>Documents:</strong> Individual source of information, magazine article, single file, email, instant message, etc...</li>
	</ul>
	<p>
		<center><img src="corpus.gif" /></center>
	</p>
	<p>
		Selecting appropriate documents to create a corpus is important for accurate results.  Questions about automobiles
		probably cannot be answered by a fashion magazine.
